caption: It's amazing.  I've been here for half an hour.  The counter keeps filling up with orders of food.  And yet none of the three people here ahead of me has been able to take away his order.  They take orders; they receive payment; they prepare the food, and they stack the food on the counter.  But they never actually serve it.
